metadata.name: Submerged_olivia1
metadata.description:
Portrait of a person just under the surface.
Saturated still.  
Christina works with water as one of her recurring elements. She wishes to reflect on personal identities many facets. She most often records herself, in a set up under water. She works the digital files changing colors, orientation and more.  Christina Maj Lundqvist works with video, photography, painting, light sculptures etc.
